			<br>&nbsp;<u><i><font color="#FFFF00">ANALOG / DIGITAL CONTROLLERS CONTROLS:</font></i></u><br>
                  &nbsp; Steer:
                  <font color="#00FF00">&nbsp;D-Pad or Left Analog Stick</font>
